Package: nightowl
Title: Statistical Visualization and Analysis for Clinical Research
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joel",
           family = "Sponer", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joel.sponer@example.com")
Description: Provides a declarative plotting system built on ggplot2 with R6 classes, 
    survival analysis capabilities, and interactive visualizations for clinical research 
    applications. Features include Kaplan-Meier curves, Cox proportional hazards modeling, 
    forest plots, and comprehensive statistical summaries with customizable styling.
URL: https://joelgsponer.github.io/nightowl/
BugReports: https://github.com/joelgsponer/nightowl/issues
